  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick skillet over medium heat.",
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine flour, baking powder, and sugar.",
    "Add melted butter, milk, hazelnuts, sweetener (if using), and vanilla extract to the dry ingredients. Mix until well combined.",
    "Pour batter onto preheated skillet and cook for 2-3 minutes per side or until bubbles form on top.",
    "Serve hot with additional toppings like fresh berries or whipped cream if desired."
